c: 35
v: 43
t: "Kubera amanyama yabo kuri iy’Isi nukugira akajagari kabi kabi, nako kajagari kabi kabi ntikamanuka atari kuri beneko bakagize, none hari ikindi barorereye atari urutonde rwamyeho no ku bantu baho hambere, kandi ntuzoronka ihindagurika ry’urwo rutonde rusanzwe rw’Imana yagenye, canke ntuzosanga ihindagurika riri mubintu bisanzwe vy’Imana"